# [IPSECME](../wg/ipsecme.html)

## Summary

The IPSECME Working Group met at IETF 126. The session covered the status of active working group documents, followed by presentations and technical discussions on SHA-3 integration, RFC 9370 ADDKE algorithm improvements, FrodoKEM for IKEv2, multi-authentication, hybrid post-quantum (PQ) and traditional authentication, composite key exchanges over reliable transport, PQC IKEv2 authentication analysis, and MLS integration for IPsec group key management.

---

